HEADWORD: Cycadales
<hw>Cycadales</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an order of primitive tropical
gymnosperms abundant in the Mesozoic, now reduced to a few scattered
tropical forms.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order <ord>Cycadales</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
